\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 -\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94So you take bribes.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 -\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94If that\u8217\'92s the way you want to put it.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 -\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94You\u8217\'92ve changed, Leto. Your pride would have never come to this.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 -\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94We don\u8217\'92t all have your monklike constitution, Zima. Every upholder of the law has to know when to let things slide.\u8221\'94\line   -\u8221\'94I seem to recall you let Vesna go when she let dozens of innocents die. Why didn\u8217\'92t you arrest her?\u8221\'94}
