\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 -\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94Besides, you let one casino close and another pops up in its place. At least with a Just around things can\u8217\'92t get out of hand.\u8221\'94}
